<plot>The inspiring account of one church and one pastor who said that the love of God and love of partner were worth standing up for. This powerful documentary chronicles the story of St. John's Lutheran Church in Atlanta, who faced a discipline, trial, and a national church because its gay pastor, Bradley Schmeling, found the love of his life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?262541</url></doc>
